data.description: Welcome to your new lake home! This modern house on a hill is situated on a LARGE .43 acre lot just around the corner from Wonder Lake. Drive up to the house, step onto the deck and take a look around. The front yard is HUGE and the hill offers privacy from the neighbors without making you feel isolated. Walk across the front deck and step inside. The first floor bathroom is to your left and to your right is a multi-purpose room can be anything you'd like! It can be a formal dining room, playroom, living room, den, craft room, etc. Custom built-in cabinets line the back wall for extra storage. There is a pass-through window into the front room from the kitchen. Step back into the hallway and continue into the beautifully renovated kitchen. Everything shines in this kitchen with its modern finishes. The butcher block island features extra storage and a 5 burner stove with a modern stainless steel hood. The white quartz countertops and white cabinets brighten the whole room. The laundry area is in the kitchen nook. Straight ahead is the utility room. To the left is the first floor bedroom with a large closet. Continue towards the back of the house and into the cozy living room. The brick feature wall has a woodburning gas fireplace perfect for a night in after a day at the Lake. There is a sliding door that leads to a fenced in area of the yard at the back of the living room. Continue upstairs. To the right is the second bedroom and to the left is the large primary bedroom. There is an adjoining bathroom between the rooms. From the primary bedroom, step outside and onto a small deck that leads down into the fenced in yard. For a video walkthrough, please visit you-tube and type in the address. This home is in a prime location just seconds from Wonder Lake and minutes from Keystone Landing and Glacial Park.  Wonder Lake is a private Lake and so great for those that live in the area.
